tioned<br />\nThe painting sold for $1.4 million before it shredded itself<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iiO_1XRnMt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiiO_1XRnMt4&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1wVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=c76e986f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iiO_1XRnMt4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/7/17947744/banksy-ballon-girl-artwork-self-destructed-sothbys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2018%2F10%2F7%2F17947744%2Fbanksy-ballon-girl-artwork-self-destructed-sothbys&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1wVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=454bc954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/7/17947744/banksy-ballon-girl-artwork-self-destructed-sothbys</a>"},{"pid":"70affb4a73383cde661b8d9449ccc1622e012d33","tid":2328576,"uid":97340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"幅嘢可唔可以改叫 我究竟睇左d乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06c71120bd7802a61976c75597b0cde3fca6922","tid":2328576,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698665d3fcfe22a41895235c1d803bcc28887e41","tid":2328576,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"令我諗起呢單嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOne of Banksy&rsquo;s paintings self-destructed just after it was auctioned<br />\nThe painting sold for $1.4 million before it shredded itself<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iiO_1XRnMt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiiO_1XRnMt4&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1wVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=c76e986f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iiO_1XRnMt4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/7/17947744/banksy-ballon-girl-artwork-self-destructed-sothbys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u